title: Salvador Dalí & Watch Enamel Pin Set
description:
Salvador Dalí and his Melting Watch make your day more surreal.

This enamel pin set is packaged with rubber pin backs. Wear your heart on your sleeve and big ideas on your collar, your hat, and your backpack for a little inspiration everywhere you go.

  • Dimensions: Card 3.15 x 0.39 x 4.33 in, Pins approx. 1.25 in. tall
  • Materials: Made of brass with black nickel plating, and hard enamel coloring
